subtitleNullable: Cars License Plates (Iran's Format) for CLP-Detection and OCR
descriptionNullable:
844 Cars License Plates (Iran's Format) for CLP-Detection and OCR 

This Dataset is in COCO format. You can change the format to others using Roboflow for Real-time Detection (YOLO) and etc.

also, you can use Augmentation to increase the images up to 2000.

**This Dataset will be updated every month to add new cars. if you wish to help in this process please get in touch with me:**
